The article is a transcript of remarks made by President Xi Jinping of China and President Donald Trump of the United States during President Trump's state visit to China. President Xi welcomes President Trump and highlights the historic progress made in China-U.S. relations over the past 45 years. Both leaders emphasize the importance of cooperation and partnership between the two countries, and express optimism for the future. The article concludes with a toast to the friendship between China and the United States.